<td style="text-align: center"><b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Atheism" title="Portal:Atheism"><small>Atheism Portal</small></a></b> ·&#160;<span class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="white-space:nowrap; font-weight:normal; font-size:xx-small;&#160;;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Atheism2" title="Template:Atheism2"><span title="View this template" style=";">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Atheism2" title="Template talk:Atheism2"><span style="color:#002bb8;;" title="Discussion about this template">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Atheism2&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Atheism2&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span style="color:#002bb8;;" title="You can edit this template. Please use the preview button before saving.">e</span></a></span>&#160;</td>
